PersonalMission.Name: TD-12: Big Game Hunting
PersonalMission.Description: Armed with your wits and an excellent gun, you can destroy enemy vehicles before they get close. Once an enemy heavy tank has been spotted, you can cause a lot of damage to them before they even spot you.
PersonalMission.Hint: You have the potential to carry your team to victory. If you know the weak spots of enemy heavy tanks, the thickness of their armor cannot save them.

Primary.Conditions:
•  Destroy a heavy tank 1 tier higher
•  Cause 2,000 HP of damage
